Combat Summary: {
  "narration": "At dawn atop the North Tower Overlook, Eirik Hearthwise and Scout Kira faced off against two hardened bandits intent on reclaiming the ruins. The battle was fierce and swift. Kira's initial arrow missed, and the bandits pressed their attack, severely wounding Kira. Eirik responded quickly with Healing Word, restoring her vitality, then struck back with his mace, wounding the aggressor. The bandits retaliated, landing a crossbow bolt into Eirik's side, but the duo held fast. Kira rallied, landing a decisive shortsword strike that felled one bandit. Eirik then cast Sacred Flame, scorching the last foe who desperately closed in. As the bandit attempted to flee Kira's blades, Eirik's final mace blow brought him crashing down, concluding the fight. Two bandit corpses lay scattered on the battered stones while the dawn chorus returned. The party earned a total of 50 experience points for vanquishing their foes, divided equally between Eirik and Kira (25 XP each). The North Tower Overlook was secured--for now.",
  "combat_round": 3,
